==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Eight and nine are not separated from ten.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: bā jĭu bù lí shí

===Adjective===
'''[[八]][[九]][[不]][[离]][[十]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') almost
#: ''[[目前]][[已]][[有]][[人]][[猜]][[得]]“'''八九不离十'''”[[了]]！！ '' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

#: ''[[目前]][[已]][[有]][[人]][[猜]][[得]]“'''八九不離十'''”[[了]]！！ '' ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Alternate forms===
[[八]][[九]][[不]][[離]][[十]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

